    "茉莉奶绿":"Jasmine milk green",
    "七窖茉莉香气馥郁端正，制成奶茶清甜怡人，浓郁奶香和茉莉花香经唇入喉，淡雅香气经久留存。":"The aroma of Qijiao jasmine is fragrant and upright, making the milk tea sweet and pleasant. The rich milk fragrance and jasmine flower fragrance pass through the lips and enter the throat, and the elegant fragrance remains for a long time.",
    "铁观音奶冻":"Tieguanyin Milk Jelly",
    "铁观音自带清雅兰香，搭配嫩滑奶冻，带来清爽又兼具浓郁奶香的丰富滋味。":"Tieguanyin has its own elegant orchid fragrance, and paired with tender milk jelly, it brings a refreshing and rich taste with rich milky aroma.",
    "黄金椰椰乌龙":"Golden coconut oolong",
    "岩韵奇兰奶茶底蕴含绵远花香与豆香，入喉茶味香醇，加入Q弹椰果为茶香增添了无限玩味。":"The base of Yanyun Qilan milk tea contains lingering floral and bean aromas, and the tea tastes mellow when it enters the throat. The addition of Q-bombed coconut adds infinite fun to the tea aroma.",
    "桂花酒酿奶绿":"Osmanthus Rice Wine Matcha Latte",
    "精选一年一季的优质五常糯米搭配桂林金桂，酿出微醺甜润，融入七窖茉莉茶底，口感更轻盈。":"Selected high-quality Wuchang glutinous rice from all over the year is paired with Guilin golden osmanthus to create a slightly sweet and slightly intoxicating taste. It is blended with the Qijiao jasmine tea base for a lighter taste.",
    "芝芝绿妍茶后":"Zhizhi Green Tea Queen",
    "2012年首创第一杯芝士茶。定制绿茶底，融入真牛乳。":"In 2012, the first cup of cheese tea was created. Customized green tea base, blended with real milk.",
    "青稞牛乳茶":"Highland barley milk tea",
    "经典嫣红牛乳茶加入软糯有嚼劲的青稞，入口奶香、茶香醇醇鲜明，还带有淡淡自然青稞麦香。":"The classic Yanhong Cow Milk Tea is made with soft, chewy and chewy highland barley. It has a milky and mellow aroma of tea and a light natural barley aroma.",
    "超清爽柠打绿":"Super refreshing lemon and green",
    "优选新鲜柠檬，每日鲜切暴打，融合甄选茶园定制绿茶汤，酸甜沁爽。":"Fresh lemons are selected, freshly cut and beaten every day, and blended with selected green tea soup from the tea garden, which is sour, sweet and refreshing.",
    "青提柠绿茶":"Qingti lemon green tea",
    "优选阳光玫瑰青提，颗颗精细去皮，加入暴打新鲜柠檬，融合绿茶底。":"Sunny rose green grapes are selected, finely peeled, beaten with fresh lemon, and blended with green tea base.",
    "米布丁珍珠大红袍":"Rice Pudding Pearl Dahongpao",
    "大师定制武夷山大红袍，13道工序传承东方岩韵，花香焙火香浑然天成。":"The master customized the Wuyi Mountain Dahongpao. The 13-step process inherits the charm of Oriental rock. The fragrance of flowers and roasted fire is natural.",
    "碧螺知春拿铁":"Biluo Zhichun Latte",
    "优选碧螺知春茶底，呈现花香蜜韵。":"Biluozhichun tea base is selected, showing floral and honey notes.",
    "茉莉海盐拿铁":"Jasmine Sea Salt Latte",
    "源自广西横州双瓣茉莉，六窨一提工艺，香气升级。":"Originating from double-petal jasmine in Hengzhou, Guangxi, it uses six scenting and one lifting techniques to upgrade the aroma.",
